Templates can be used and created as follow
1. make a folder called templates in the same folder as the flask app
2. in the method add the render_template('name.html', pass in the variables, variables)

By defaurlt a route in flask only responds to get requests. 


Steps to fix a bug in your code: 
	1. Find what the error log says.
	2. look at the line of code and ask yourself what does it return.
	3. trace back the return value to the source or the next object and repeat. 

	